{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4855c92c9a","title":"中央转发北京市委关于摧毁一贯道的报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"62b92d00ce","index":0,"year":1951,"month":2,"day":28,"articleId":"4855c92c9a"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""},{"id":"maoquanji30","name":"毛泽东全集第30卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/30-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3712f3d2db","type":"title","text":"中央转发北京市委关于摧毁一贯道的报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"4855c92c9a"},{"id":"0ffc32eaee","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"4855c92c9a"},{"id":"321c7ba481","type":"appellation","text":"各中央局，并转所属分局，省委，大中市委，区党委：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"4855c92c9a"},{"id":"b736de1574","type":"paragraph","text":"关于摧毁一贯道，北京的经验是很成功的。一是长期侦察布置，不是仓促举行；二是临事向群众宣传，孤立道首；三是布置展览会；四是退道款；五是与反迷信分开。以上各项可作各地参考。一贯道在全国有几百万被欺骗的落后群众，各省凡有大批一贯道存在的地方，党对这个问题的处理必须采取慎重和适当的态度。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"4855c92c9a"},{"id":"d931dc04ed","type":"paragraph","text":" 中央二月廿八日","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"4855c92c9a"}],"page":{"id":"97d531312f","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"4855c92c9a","start":0,"end":0}},"maoquanji30":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"40d305fab3","type":"title","text":"中央转发北京市委关于摧毁一贯道的报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"4855c92c9a"},{"id":"45e7910515","type":"paragraph","text":"各中央局，并转所属分局，省委，大中市委，区党委：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"4855c92c9a"},{"id":"ef72c6e58d","type":"paragr